
NuBonjour is a collection of classes that help Nu programs connect over Bonjour.

Contents:
  NuBonjour  - a component that builds as a framework for the Mac and a static library for the iPhone
  Client     - a Nu-based application that can be used to connect to and interact with an iPhone using NuBonjour.
  background - preliminary work that led to NuBonjour

Released under the Apache 2.0 license. 

NuBonjour is built on AGSocket. AGSocket source files (AG*) are included and released under their original license.

Tim Burks
